Before generating documentation, enforce:

* Section order is correct.
* No empty tables.
* No multi-sentence descriptions.
* No undocumented exported symbol.
* No undocumented exported enum value.
* No undocumented exported type field.
* No additional sections.
* No trailing commentary.

If a section has zero items, omit the section entirely.

